
How to install Go Lang in Kali.

Open CMD:

sudo apt update

sudo apt upgrade

*****************************

sudo apt install golang-go

echo $PATH

go env | grep GOPATH  # copy go path and paste into .zshrc

nano ~/.zshrc

export PATH="$PATH:********/bin"

source ~/.zshrc

********************************
sudo rm /usr/bin/httpx

---------------------------------------------------------------------------


Update Python Version in Kali Linux 2019.2

https://exitcode0.net/kali-linux-how-to-upgrade-python-2-7-to-python-3-7/

From Terminal:
        Open Terminal
        ls /usr/bin/python*
        alias python='/usr/bin/python3.8'
        python --version
        
        OR
        
        update-alternatives --config python
